headline: Rothschild upgrades Kenvue after Tylenol scare wipes $10 billion in market value
summary: Investing.com -- Rothschild upgraded Kenvue to Buy, saying a U.S. health regulator’s plans for new warning labels on Tylenol were less severe than feared and that the consumer health company’s 20% stock drop this month had overshot the risk.Shares are up 1.5% in premarket trading.
